      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that the interest adds up, but you called it a \"sneaky little troll\"... that's a weird way to put it. can you just stick to the math? specifically, can you show me the actual formula they use to calculate that monthly interest so i can see exactly how much is being taken out before it even hits the principal?",
